description: Peak Season Pops the innovated idea of a health educator and professional cook couple from Winter Park, Florida. Their idea of handcrafting popsicles by utilizing peak ingredients from every season led to the creation of endless combinations of flavors. The season changing popsicles range from a mojito popsicle in the spring to a pumpkin apple spice peel in the fall. There is something for your enjoyment all year round. Check them out at the local farmers market or book them for your next special event, they even have popsicles for your pup!
name: Peak Season Pop
